Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌方拒绝停战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪兵队退下，改用炮击战
