Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.19,0:19:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯战舰三艘沉没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方舰队胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.17,0:19:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一架先锋艇要求登舰许可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,念给我听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.68,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有书信要交付旗舰克劳索拉斯\N舰长大卫．麦德赛大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.48,0:19:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是诺齐亚先锋艇组织所属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.05,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士．沃卡以及拉薇．海德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登舰许可下来了\N从后方甲板登舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走啰，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,技术不差哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.58,0:20:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是克劳士．沃卡\N感谢允许我们登舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉薇．海德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问…你们赢了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.89,0:20:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然\N我们麦德赛舰队大获全胜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错了，走右边啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿玛达号！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.81,0:20:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.39,0:21:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报告损伤情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.69,0:21:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特梅雷亚号中弹沉没中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是度西斯的残余舰队吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，从上空出现了\N未经登记的舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是违反协定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安斯维拉号失去航行能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.72,0:21:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔特公会在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.24,0:21:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骑士精神…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.94,0:21:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说大获全胜吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.48,0:22:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，难道不是吗
