Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.01,0:24:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是吃太多\N吃得脑浆都变猪油啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.61,0:24:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猪油？
